messages.text:
Hey, sorry I didn't recognize you in the lobby this morning. I'm sure I'll get to know you eventually. Maybe after I get back from my trip to Tahiti?

Well, listen. Times are rough. Profit only increased by 10% last year. I know, I know, horrible. And I had to let half of our junior staffers go just to get that 10%!

So I'll cut right to the chase. I need money. And championships. Money and championships, that's what I'm interested in.

Get it done.

events.text: The Wizards traded Bradley Beal to the Grizzlies for Kyle Anderson, Ja Morant, Josh Jackson, a 2020 1st round pick (MEM), a 2022 2nd round pick (CHI), and a 2022 2nd round pick (MEM).
The Wizards traded John Wall and a 2022 2nd round pick (CHI) to the Pistons for Langston Galloway, Reggie Jackson, Bruce Brown Jr, and Luke Kennard.
The Timberwolves traded Andrew Wiggins and Jordan Bell to the 76ers for Tobias Harris.
The Wizards traded Davis Bertans and Reggie Jackson to the 76ers for Al Horford and a 2021 1st round pick (PHI).
The Timberwolves traded Jarrett Culver and a 2020 1st round pick (MIN) to the Knicks for Kris Wilkes and Dennis Smith.
